short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Extension to get the code of SVG assets from Webflow asset manager.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
The extension allows you to get the code of SVG assets from the Webflow asset manager.

Instructions to use:
When you open SVG image settings, you will automatically see the "Copy SVG Code" option in the assets panel.

We are working on more improvements for Webflow users.

For help, reach out to hello@littlebigthings.dev
